widgets.title: avg http response vs. error logs & spans
Checkly Synthetics - Frontend Avg API Checks (seconds)

dataprimeQuery.text:
source logs
| filter $l.applicationname == 'default' && $l.subsystemname == 'frontend'
| groupby $d.product_id_enriched.category as $d.product_category aggregate  sum($d.product_id_enriched.price_in_currency:num) as $d.total_price
| filter $d.product_category != null

source logs
| filter $l.applicationname == 'default' && $l.subsystemname == 'frontend'
| groupby $d.product_id_enriched.category as $d.product_category aggregate  sum($d.product_id_enriched.price_in_currency:num) as $d.total_price
| filter $d.product_category != null

source spans
| filter tags['db.system'] == 'redis'
| filter tags['db.statement'] != null
| groupby tags['db.redis.flags'] as flags, $l.operationName as action avg(duration)/1000 as span_duration_seconds
| orderby span_duration_seconds desc

source spans
| filter tags['db.system'] == 'redis'
| filter tags['db.statement'] != null
| groupby tags['db.redis.database_index'] as database_index, tags['db.redis.flags'] as flags, $l.operationName as action, tags['db.statement'] avg(duration)/1000 as span_duration_seconds
| orderby span_duration_seconds desc

widgets.title: Top 10 Requests per Second by IP Address

dataprimeQuery.text:
source logs 
| filter $l.subsystemname == 'frontend' 
| filter $d.json.http_req_ip != null
| timeround $m.timestamp to 1s into $d.second 
| groupby json.http_req_ip as ip_address, $d.second aggregate count() as logs_per_second
| groupby ip_address aggregate avg($d.logs_per_second) as avg_requests_per_second
| orderby avg_requests_per_second desc
